description_schinese: 获得后由客户端处理立刻转换为特定角色亲密度

name: Normal Torch
description: Default Torch
description_schinese: 初始火把

name: Divine Comedy
description: Weapons from hell are always accompanied by fire. Don’t ask why it’s a fork, and don’t ask why you eat buns with a fork. Those who dare to ask will never see the sun tomorrow. You should show some respect to the great demon!
description_schinese: 来自地狱的武器永远与烈火为伴，别问怎么是个叉子，也别问为什么拿叉子吃馍馍，敢问的都见不到明天的太阳了。你应当对伟大的恶魔展现出一些尊重！

name: Primary Wand
description: The entry-level wand does not have any cool shape, it seems to be the product of rough processing of special trees. But this is still a staff, no matter how it is burned, it will not change in any way, because it is too strong, sometimes it will be used for physical attacks?
description_schinese: 入门级的法杖没有什么炫酷造型，似乎只是选取了特殊树木进行粗略加工后的产物。不过这依然是法杖，无论怎么被火烧都不会有任何改变，由于实在太结实，有时候也会被拿来进行物理攻击的样子？

name: candlestick
description: The little clever ghost who dismantled his own candlestick and used it as a torch will be beaten by his parents when he returns home.
description_schinese: 把自家烛台拆了拿来当火把的小机灵鬼，回家要被爹妈混合双打。

name: Magic
description: This is a special torch, full of magic. As for your question about its magic, the flame will magically change its color, which is very powerful, and it is not a useless function!
description_schinese: 这是一个特别的火把，充满了魔法。至于你问它的神奇之处在哪，火焰会神奇地改变颜色，很厉害哦，才不是毫无用处的功能呢！

name: Windproof
description: The torch that has been strengthened and modified by the blacksmith has a special structure, which is more difficult to be blown out by the wind than ordinary torches, and is a must-have for explorers when going out.
description_schinese: 经过铁匠铺加固和改造的火把有特殊构造，比起一般的火把更难被风吹灭，是探险家出门必备之物。

name: Orange Lollipop
description: If you eat too much, your tongue will turn into an orange lollipop, but this one seems like you can't finish licking it anyway, huh? Why can I smell gunpowder?
description_schinese: 吃多了舌头会变成橙色的棒棒糖，不过这一根似乎无论如何都舔不完的样子，咦？为什么能闻到一股火药味？

name: The touch of the cannon and the demonic flower
Yellow broad-rimmed hat
description: Clothes from the frontier of the southern country, wide-brimmed hats woven from bamboo strips and reed leaves, exist instead of umbrellas. Over the years, the original green color has receded.
description_schinese: 出自南国边疆的服饰，由竹篾和箬叶编织的宽边帽，代替雨伞而存在。多年过去，原本青绿的色彩都退去了。

name: county viceroy
description: Purity of heart is the root cause, and straightness is personal strategy.
description_schinese: 清心为治本，直道是身谋。

name: Pingtian crown
description: The crown of sacrificial clothing, from the emperor to the corporals and deacons, is worn by all, and is specially distinguished by the number of beams and the number of crowns. It is commonly called the Pingtian Crown.
description_schinese: 祭服之冕，自天子至于下士执事者，皆服之，特以梁数及旒之多少为别，俗呼为平天冠。

name: Apprentice hats
description: The hats, ribbons and gold medals specially prepared for students who have just started learning spells are very eye-catching, and such bright colors can be noticed from a long distance, so that everyone can hide away.
description_schinese: 专门为刚开始学习法术的学生准备的帽子，丝带和金牌非常醒目，很远就能注意到这样明亮的颜色，方便大家躲远点走。

name: centre parting
description: Grandma's gray tinfoil ironed her hair, and the handsome figure playing basketball must have fascinated you.
description_schinese: 奶奶灰锡纸烫中分头，打篮球的帅气身影一定把你狠狠迷住了吧。

name: Thunder cloud
description: Don't talk to me, I want to be quiet...
description_schinese: 别和我讲话，我想静静……

name: Herald cap.
description: The brown camouflage hat can effectively block the sun in the wilderness. Wearing it and lying between the sand and stones has a self-invisibility effect. If you don’t want the hair on the top of your head to be blown off by the strong wind, you’d better fasten the belt honestly.
description_schinese: 棕色迷彩帽在荒原里可以有效遮挡阳光，戴着它趴在砂石之间简直自带隐身效果，不想被大风吹掉头顶的毛的话，还是老老实实系好带子吧。

name: Yellow duck
description: The cute hat that the cubs like can not only prevent the rain, but also can make the heart of Furui pass by when a row of little guys wobble past after school.
description_schinese: 幼崽喜欢的可爱帽子，不仅能防雨，放学时一排小家伙摇摇晃晃走过时可以萌化路过的福瑞心。

name: vampire wings
description: There are always cubs who think they can fly with these wings on their backs, and there are not a few of them who break their bones, so it was once a taboo attire. Perhaps some unknown existence really cursed it, and even the tail would change shape after wearing it.
description_schinese: 总有幼崽觉得背上这对翅膀就能飞起来，摔骨折的不在少数，因此一度成为禁忌的装束。或许是真的有某种未知存在诅咒了它吧，穿戴上后连尾巴都会跟着改变形状。

name: DaShu Bag
description: The sun was shining, the flowers smiled at me, and the little bird said early, why are you carrying explosives... sorry, big schoolbag.
description_schinese: 太阳当空照，花儿对我笑，小鸟说早早早，你为什么背着炸药……对不起，大书包。

name: Kun Cape
description: The clothes that can only be obtained after hard training are awarded by a certain Yu clan teacher who crows in the morning.
description_schinese: 经过辛苦训练才能领到的衣服，由某位早上打鸣的羽族老师颁发。

name: Yellow Robe
description: Yellow, the color of neutrality, the property of nature, never changes.
description_schinese: 黄者，中和之色，自然之性，万古不易。

name: Straw Rain Cape
description: Furui in the southern frontier often use coir rain cape and straw hat together. The coats woven with palm skin are not only rainproof but also warm.
description_schinese: 南国边疆的福瑞们往往将蓑衣和箬笠搭配使用，棕榈皮编织的大衣不仅防雨还能保暖。

name: Viceroy
description: I don't seek fame or salary, what I seek is to fight for some justice for the unfortunate people in the world, and to leave some awe-inspiring righteousness for the court.
description_schinese: 吾既不求名，也不谋禄，所求者只为天地间不幸之人争些公平义理，为庙堂上留些凛然正气。

name: Tiny bear
description: It seems that every little Furui has a doll to lull children to sleep.
description_schinese: 哄孩子睡觉的玩偶，似乎每个小福瑞都有过一个。

name: black cat
description: Cats are so cute, they can cry for a long time with one punch.
description_schinese: 猫猫这么可爱，打一拳能哭好久吧。

name: Boomer
description: There is a sense of urgency with it on your back, and something bad will happen if you don't run fast!
description_schinese: 背上它就会有一种紧迫感，不跑快点的话会发生不妙的事！

name: Universal Bag
description: I don't know where I picked up the bag, and it still contains the empty bottles collected so hard. Will Furui be anxious after losing the bag?
description_schinese: 不知道从哪捡来的袋子，里面还装着辛辛苦苦收集来的空瓶子，丢了袋子的福瑞会着急吗？

name: Adventure Bag
description: The huge backpack can hold a lot of things. With such a bag, experienced pioneers found an oasis in the desert and established the first station. All the essentials for an expedition are quickly found and available, from lamps for lighting, to bedding for sleeping, and even room for fossils found along the way.
description_schinese: 巨大的背包能装下许多东西，经验丰富的先行者凭借这样的包在大漠中找到了绿洲，建立起第一个驿站。所有探险的必备物品都能迅速找到并取用，从照明的灯，到睡觉的铺盖，甚至有地方装路上发现的化石。

name: MingYueBenWuXin
description_schinese: 中秋馈礼赠送物品

name: Empty Footprint
description: None Footprint
description_schinese: 空足迹

name: Hell wander
description: Wherever you go, the ground will crack, and the lava will become your mark. The fabled horrors are banned from the surface because they will only made buns be  more expensive if they live in the world.
description_schinese: 所行之处地表都将开裂，熔岩将成为你的印记。传说中的恐怖生物被禁止来到地面，因为它们活在世上只会把馍吃贵。
